913,"Нарратив как самотерапия тревоги","<!-- StartFragment -->
<table style=""font-family: Arial, Verdana; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; width: 100%; border-width: 0px;"" cellspacing=""0"" cellpadding=""0"">
